data.description: OWNERS WANT OFFERS! This charming home is a must-see! Standout features include a large lot with raised gardens, plenty of natural light, kitchen granite countertops, wood burning fireplace, upstairs family/game room, updated owner suite bathroom, and water softener and filtration system. A/C unit replaced in 2020, new backyard fencing and garage door. Convenient commute location, near restaurants and Buda City Parks. Schedule a showing today and don't miss your opportunity to make this home yours. *Seller's are offering a $8k concession to help buy down the interest rate. This home qualifies for a federal tax credit.
